      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GUS THE JET (8) is a super honest type rarely out of the placings, including wins at his last two on end, the latest at Capalaba (19.97). Form at the trip excellent including three wins. Boxed wide but will go close with the right run. MAGIC SHAZAM (2) goes very well this trip starting 13 times for five wins and five minors. Missed the frame latest (22.13) when seventh over 390m at this track in a OPEN. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. SEAWAY CRUISER (1) pinged the lids and was in the firing line early but drifted out of it when 5th at this track in Grade 5 company. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Likely to be about the money.",
